fg_segments: Chicago Botanic Garden Web Site, 1000 Lake Cook Road, Glencoe, IL 60022.How is
My Online Information Used?Our online privacy policy is simple: we don't sell, barter, give away or rent your e-mail to any outside organization.
For each visitor to our web page, our web server automatically recognizes only the consumer's domain name and e-mail address (where possible).
We collect aggregate information on what pages consumers access or visit.
The information we collect is used to improve the content of our Web page and is not shared with other organizations.
Email CommunicationsWe provide free eNewsletters to keep you up-to-date on Chicago Botanic Garden programs and events.
We do not sell, rent or share your email information with anyone.
You can subscribe and unsubscribe to receive this information at anytime.
If you do not want to receive e-mail from us in the future, please let us know by writing to us at the above address and telling us that you do not want to receive e-mail from our organization.
Opt-out and Correction Procedures You always may opt-out of receiving future email messages and enewsletters.
You can stop receiving email communications from us at any time by selecting the "unsubscribe" text link provided at the bottom of all email communications.
We also permit you to correct or update personal information that you have previously provided to us.
SurveysWe deploy surveys online and on location (in order to get information) to help us understand our audience.
You may decide whether or not you want to answer our survey questions.
No personal information from these surveys is disclosed to third party organizations.
SecurityThe Chicago Botanic Garden makes every effort to ensure that its Web site is secure.
For the protection of transactions on the Web site, the Garden uses the industry standard 128-bit secure socket layer (SSL) protocol.
Socket layer technology encrypts your credit card information to prevent it from being decoded by anyone but the Chicago Botanic Garden.
If you prefer, you may phone or fax your order.
